        <h1>Fitness Plan (40-65 Underweight)</h1>
        
        <h2>Diet Plan</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Whole grain toast with peanut butter and banana slices.</li>
            <li><strong>Lunch:</strong> Grilled salmon with quinoa and steamed asparagus.</li>
            <li><strong>Snacks:</strong> Almonds, cashews, and a protein shake.</li>
            <li><strong>Dinner:</strong> Lentil soup with whole wheat bread and mixed greens.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Gym Routine</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Strength training (low-impact, bodyweight exercises) 3-4 times a week.</li>
            <li>Light cardio (brisk walking, cycling) 3 times a week.</li>
            <li>Flexibility and balance exercises (yoga, stretching) daily.</li>
        </ul>
